fields.description:
I'm seeing failures when running import instance using 13G windows images in my automated test runs. The same test using 3G Linux images is working fine. Opening this to track/debug.  
Thanks,
-M

image url and euca-tools request made from the clc (via eutester):

{code}
http://mirror.eucalyptus-systems.com/images/windows_images/golden_images/windows7_winrm_3_4_0.img

euca-tools command:
source eucarc-10.111.5.63-eucalyptus-admin/eucarc && euca-import-instance /disk1/storage/windows7_winrm_3_4_0.img -b import_instance_test_bucket -z PARTI00 -f raw -t c1.medium -a x86_64 -p Windows --show-empty-fields  -g import_instance_test_group --key import_instance_test_key1412889509 --user-data "#cloud-config
disable_root: false"
{code}
